            <title>[SOLR-16445] Replica leader message should be sent when there is more than one (NRT+Tlog) replica)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16445</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, solr does leader election when there is more than one replica. But it does consider pull replica as well, which doesn&apos;t take part in leader election. Also optimize this behavior for PRS collection.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m marking this issue as major to see if we can fix in 9.0&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
